---
title: Carb Smart Cheesy Bacon-Stuffed Zucchini Boats with Italian-Dressed Salad
description: These zucchini boats are stuffed with a mixture of cheese, bacon and breadcrumbs before getting baked to glorious golden perfection. A fresh side salad with a garlicky dressing  and crispy shallots kicks things up a notch!
